## Description {#details}

Represents overflowing add/sub operations.

Only carry-out: G&#95;UADDO, G&#95;SADDO, G&#95;USUBO, G&#95;SSUBO Carry-in and carry-out: G&#95;UADDE, G&#95;SADDE, G&#95;USUBE, G&#95;SSUBE
